Read existing notes on a lead — context the human team or prior agent runs have already captured.

{{include:headers/tool-when-to-use}} before adding a note via leadbay_report_outreach, to avoid duplicating or overwriting context the SDR already wrote.

{{include:headers/tool-when-not-to-use}} when the lead summary's `notes_count` is 0 — there's nothing to fetch.
